Obsidian Image Clipper
======================

This project contains code derived from Local Images Plus:

  https://github.com/Sergei-Korneev/obsidian-local-images-plus

Local Images Plus is licensed under the MIT License. Its license text is kept
in apps/obsidian-plugin/LICENSE.

Obsidian Image Clipper adds browser Cookie sync, native host integration,
exact-domain authenticated downloads, diagnostics, packaging, and public
project documentation around that upstream base.
